These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: rock-climbing, board-games, woodworking, skydiving
1. Hobby:board-games is in an odd position##4
2. Hobby:skydiving is between Hobby:rock-climbing and Hobby:board-games##2
3. Hobby:skydiving is on the right of Hobby:rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Game: chess, snooker, whist, scrabble
1. Game:chess is on the left of Game:scrabble##1
2. Game:snooker is in an odd position##4
3. Game:snooker is on the left or right of Game:chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Game   | snooker | chess | scrabble | whist |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
