.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-18::.
Birthday: july, december, august, january
1. Birthday:august is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:december is on the far left or far right##3
3. Birthday:august is between Birthday:december and Birthday:july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | january | july | august | december |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Hobby: camping, fishing, board-games, video-games
1. Hobby:fishing == Hobby:fishing##1
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left or right of Hobby:board-games##3
3. Hobby:board-games is on the far left or far right##3
4. Hobby:camping is in an even position##4
5. Hobby:video-games is on the left of Hobby:fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games | fishing | camping |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
Pet: hedgehog, ferret, mouse, snake
1. Pet:mouse is in an odd position##4
2. Pet:snake is on the left of Pet:mouse##1
3. Pet:mouse is on the left or right of Pet:ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Pet   | hedgehog | snake | mouse | ferret |

 